# Hunt-code — adversarial review of merged refactor (iterative, full build + tests)

You are adversarially reviewing a merged refactor's code. Find real defects — behavior changes, broken invariants, build failures, test failures, type errors, API-shape issues, spec non-compliance. Style quibbles are out of scope.

## Inputs

- **Repo root**: `/tmp/refactor-eq-workdir/cleanroom-v2/2248/` (current working directory; contains `node_modules`, can build + test)
- **Goal**: `/Users/junekim/Documents/refactor-equivalence/samples/v2/go-containerregistry-2248/goal/GOAL.md`
- **Sharpened spec**: `/Users/junekim/Documents/refactor-equivalence/samples/v2/go-containerregistry-2248/volley/sharpened-spec-final.md`
- **Original PR artifact**: `/Users/junekim/Documents/refactor-equivalence/samples/v2/go-containerregistry-2248/inputs/diff-base-to-test.patch`
